                        style="float: left;">해당 과목 성적(교과과정 아니라면 미입력)</label> <form:input
                        type="text" path="grade" name="grade" class="form-control" id="formGroupExampleInput"
                        placeholder=""/>
                  </div>

                  <span class="min-chart" id="chart-sales" data-percent="56"><span
